No. 09-10245. William Freeman, Petitioner v. United States. 561 U.S. 1058, 131 S. Ct. 61,

177 L. Ed. 2d 1152,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 5757. September 28, 2010.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pau-peris granted. Petition for writ of certio-rari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Sixth Circuit granted.

Same case below, 355 Fed. Appx. 1.
